name: Jabba's Sail Barge (V)
Lore: 'Ubrikkian sail barge. Custom built for Jabba with an armored hull and weaponry. Top speed of 100 kph. Used by the Hutt crimelord on his many trips to Mos Eisley.',
Text: 'Deploys only on Tatooine. May add 1 driver and 8 passengers. Scum And Villainy may deploy aboard. During your deploy phase, may deploy one Jabba, Pote, or Passenger Deck aboard from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Immune to attrition < 6.',
